name: NEON TRIBUTE 01/10 DAFT PUNK
description:
This is the first NEON TRIBUTE token of the 10 collection.

It comes from one of the most important music groups DAFT PUNK.

Rendered in 4K using real-time technology "Eevee" 6 hours. It takes place in a nebula world with their symbolic pyramid.

- About NEON TRIBUTES -

The TRIBUTES came from historic characters, music groups and artist, pop and geek culture, specific athletes and videogames all of them inspired in 3D neon concept worlds, with the dominance of the 2 COLLECTION COLRS:

PUNK PINK: #FF0097 (255,0,151)

AWAKE BLUE: #00FFFF (0,255,255)

SPOOKY ORANGE: #FFA640 (255,166,64)

and some more original colors to come.

Hope you enjoy this exploration of our world tributes
